No. 09-1208. Charles L. Ryan, Director, Arizona Department of Corrections, Petitioner v. Laurence K. Libberton. 560 U.S. 979, 130 S. Ct. 3412,

177 L. Ed. 2d 349,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4744. June 14, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 583 F.3d 1147.
